'''天主教聖路易斯總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Sancti Ludovici}}）是[[羅馬天主教會|羅馬天主教會]]以[[美國|美國]]東部[[聖路易斯_(密蘇里州)|聖路易斯]]為中心的一個教省[[總教區|總教區]]，也是該國三十二個總教區之一。總教區管轄[[密蘇里州|密蘇里州]]東部十一縣，下轄三個教區。

總教區於2019年時有50萬5243名教友（佔總人口22.5%）、179個[[堂區|堂區]]和574名[[司鐸|司鐸]]。<ref>{{cite web |title=About the Archdiocese |url=https://www.archstl.org/about-the-archdiocese |publisher=Archdiocese of St. Louis |accessdate=2020-02-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200209182425/https://www.archstl.org/about-the-archdiocese |archivedate=2020-02-09 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>現任總主教為{{link-en|米徹爾·T·羅桑斯基|Mitchell T. Rozanski}}<ref name="Vatican20200610">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 10.06.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/06/10/200610b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-06-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610125434/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/06/10/200610b.html |archivedate=2020-06-10 |language=en |date=2020-06-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-en|馬爾谷·S·里維圖索|Mark S. Rivituso}}<ref name="leadership">{{cite web |title=Leadership |url=https://www.archstl.org/leadership |publisher=Archdiocese of St. Louis |accessdate=2020-02-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200209165510/https://www.archstl.org/leadership |archivedate=2020-02-09 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為{{link-en|羅勃·雅各伯·卡爾森|Robert James Carlson|羅勃·J·卡爾森}}<ref name="Vatican20200610" />，榮休輔理主教為{{link-en|羅勃·若瑟·赫爾門|Robert Joseph Hermann|羅勃·J·赫爾門}}<ref name="leadership" />。主教座堂為[[聖路易聖殿主教座堂|聖路易聖殿主教座堂]]。

'''聖路易斯教區'''於1826年成立<ref>{{cite web |title=History of the Archdiocese |url=https://www.archstl.org/history |publisher=Archdiocese of St. Louis |accessdate=2020-02-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200209183724/https://www.archstl.org/history |archivedate=2020-02-09 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1847年7月20日升格為總教區<ref>{{cite web |title=An Immigrant Church |url=https://www.archstl.org/history/immigrant-church |publisher=Archdiocese of St. Louis |accessdate=2020-02-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200209184007/https://www.archstl.org/history/immigrant-church |archivedate=2020-02-09 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

